<MyCoReWebPage>
  <section xml:lang="de" title="DuEPublico: Dissertationen">

    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <h3 class="panel-title">
          <i class="fa fa-graduation-cap" style="margin-right:1ex;" aria-hidden="true" />
          Ihre Dissertation online veröffentlichen
        </h3>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-body">
        <p>Die Universität Duisburg-Essen bietet ihren Doktorandinnen und Doktoranden die Möglichkeit, ihre
          Dissertationen im Volltext online über DuEPublico zu veröffentlichen.  </p>

        <ul style="list-style-type:none; padding:0;">
          <li>
            <i class="fa fa-info-circle" style="margin-right:1ex;" aria-hidden="true" />
            <div style="display:inline-block; vertical-align:top;">
              <a href="https://www.uni-due.de/ub/publikationsdienste/dissertationen.php">Allgemeine Informationen zur Veröffentlichung von Dissertationen</a>
              <br />
              Informationen zu Veröffentlichungsformen, zur Abgabe von Pflichtexemplaren in der UB und Ansprechpartner
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="fa fa-info-circle" style="margin-right:1ex;" aria-hidden="true" />
            <div style="display:inline-block; vertical-align:top;">
              <a href="https://www.uni-due.de/ub/publikationsdienste/dissertationen_elektronisch.php#Verlag">Parallel im Verlag und online veröffentlichen: Geht das?</a>
              <br />
              Zu beachten, falls Sie gleichzeitig in einem Verlag als auch online in DuEPublico veröffentlichen möchten
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <h3 class="panel-title">
          <i class="fa fa-check-square-o" style="margin-right:1ex;" aria-hidden="true" />
          Schritt für Schritt zur Online-Veröffentlichung
        </h3>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-body">
        <p>DuEPublico führt Sie schrittweise durch den Ablauf. So läuft die Online-Veröffentlichung in DuEPublico ab:
        </p>

        <ul style="list-style-type:none; padding:0;">
          <li>
            <i class="fa fa-square-o" style="margin-right:1ex;" aria-hidden="true" />
            <div style="display:inline-block; vertical-align:top;">
              <a href="requirements.xml">
                <strong>Was Sie benötigen</strong>
              </a>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="fa fa-square-o" style="margin-right:1ex;" aria-hidden="true" />
            <div style="display:inline-block; vertical-align:top;">
              <a href="../../authorization/login.xed?url=../content/diss/publish.xml">
                <strong>Sie melden sich bei DuEPublico an</strong>
              </a>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="fa fa-square-o" style="margin-right:1ex;" aria-hidden="true" />
            <div style="display:inline-block; vertical-align:top;">
              <a href="../../servlets/MCRActionMappingServlet/Diss/create">
                <strong>Sie geben die beschreibenden Daten Ihrer Dissertation ein</strong>
              </a>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="fa fa-square-o" style="margin-right:1ex;" aria-hidden="true" />
            <div style="display:inline-block; vertical-align:top;">
              <strong>Sie laden die Dateien hoch</strong>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="fa fa-square-o" style="margin-right:1ex;" aria-hidden="true" />
            <div style="display:inline-block; vertical-align:top;">
              <strong>Sie drucken das Formblatt aus und geben es unterschrieben zusammen mit zwei Ausdrucken in der UB
                ab.</strong>
              <br />
              Das Formblatt können Sie einfach vorausgefüllt nach dem Hochladen der Dateien direkt aus DuEPublico abrufen!
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="fa fa-square-o" style="margin-right:1ex;" aria-hidden="true" />
            <div style="display:inline-block; vertical-align:top;">
              <strong>Nach Prüfung schaltet die UB die Dateien in DuEPublico frei.</strong>
              <br />
              Erst dann ist Ihre Dissertation online im Volltext weltweit zugänglich.
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="fa fa-square-o" style="margin-right:1ex;" aria-hidden="true" />
            <div style="display:inline-block; vertical-align:top;">
              <strong>Die Dissertation wird an die Deutsche Nationalbibliothek übermittelt und dort archiviert.</strong>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

  </section>

  <section xml:lang="en" title="DuEPublico: Dissertationen">

    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <h3 class="panel-title">
          <i class="fa fa-graduation-cap" style="margin-right:1ex;" aria-hidden="true" />
          Publish your dissertation online
        </h3>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-body">
        <p>Doctoral candidates of Duisburg Essen University have the option to publish their dissertations as digital
          full text via DuEPublico.</p>

        <ul style="list-style-type:none; padding:0;">
          <li>
            <i class="fa fa-info-circle" style="margin-right:1ex;" aria-hidden="true" />
            <div style="display:inline-block; vertical-align:top;">
              <a href="https://www.uni-due.de/ub/en/edissertationen.php">General information on the delivery of dissertations</a>
              <br />
              Informationen on forms of publication, submission of compulsory copies of dissertations and contact
              persons

            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="fa fa-info-circle" style="margin-right:1ex;" aria-hidden="true" />
            <div style="display:inline-block; vertical-align:top;">
              <a href="https://www.uni-due.de/ub/en/edissertationen_elektronische.php#company">Simultaneous publication in a publishing company: is that possible?</a>
              <br />
              Please note if you want to publish through a publishing house als well as online by the library at the
              same time
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <h3 class="panel-title">
          <i class="fa fa-check-square-o" style="margin-right:1ex;" aria-hidden="true" />
          Step by step to the online publication
        </h3>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-body">
        <p>DuEPublico guides you step by step through the process. This is how the online publication in DuEPublico
          works:</p>

        <ul style="list-style-type:none; padding:0;">
          <li>
            <i class="fa fa-square-o" style="margin-right:1ex;" aria-hidden="true" />
            <div style="display:inline-block; vertical-align:top;">
              <a href="requirements.xml">
                <strong>What you need</strong>
              </a>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="fa fa-square-o" style="margin-right:1ex;" aria-hidden="true" />
            <div style="display:inline-block; vertical-align:top;">
              <a href="../../authorization/login.xed?url=../content/diss/publish.xml">
                <strong>You log in to DuEPublico</strong>
              </a>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="fa fa-square-o" style="margin-right:1ex;" aria-hidden="true" />
            <div style="display:inline-block; vertical-align:top;">
              <a href="../../servlets/MCRActionMappingServlet/Diss/create">
                <strong>You enter the descriptive data of your dissertation</strong>
              </a>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="fa fa-square-o" style="margin-right:1ex;" aria-hidden="true" />
            <div style="display:inline-block; vertical-align:top;">
              <strong>You upload the files</strong>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="fa fa-square-o" style="margin-right:1ex;" aria-hidden="true" />
            <div style="display:inline-block; vertical-align:top;">
              <strong>You print the form, sign it and submit it to the libryary along with two printed copies of your
                dissertation.</strong>
              <br />
              You can retrieve the pre-filled form directly from DuEPublico after uploading the files.
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="fa fa-square-o" style="margin-right:1ex;" aria-hidden="true" />
            <div style="display:inline-block; vertical-align:top;">
              <strong>After checking, the library will unlock the files in DuEPublico.</strong>
              <br />
              After that, your publication will be accessible worldwide in full text.
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <i class="fa fa-square-o" style="margin-right:1ex;" aria-hidden="true" />
            <div style="display:inline-block; vertical-align:top;">
              <strong>Your dissertation will also be transmitted to the German National Library where it will be stored
                long-term.</strong>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

  </section>

</MyCoReWebPage>
